Package: readflex
Type: Package
Title: Enhanced Flexible CSV Reader with Automatic Encoding Detection
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-06-21
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Toshihiro", "Iguchi",
      email = "toshihiro.iguchi.github@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Maintainer: Toshihiro Iguchi <toshihiro.iguchi.github@gmail.com>
Description: An advanced CSV reader that automatically detects character encodings
    and handles various file formats. Features include multi-language support,
    performance optimization with caching and parallel processing, comprehensive
    diagnostics, data validation, Shiny integration, and extensive analytics.
    Supports UTF-8, Shift_JIS, GB18030, Big5, EUC-KR, KOI8-R, Windows-1251,
    ISO-8859-1, and many other encodings commonly used worldwide.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/toshihiro-iguchi/readflex
BugReports: https://github.com/toshihiro-iguchi/readflex/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
